          "title": "Decorate your Thanksgiving table like a pro with these 4 ideas",
          "body": "For this look we wanted to highlight the juxtaposition of the bright orange with the classic blue and white chinoiserie for a chic and preppy feel. Gold accents tie in the colors of the season and present as the perfect partners for this palette, highlighting its warmth with a glow that silver just couldn't have accomplished.\n\nDainty orange pumpkins are piled high at each place setting and mirror the orange tones found in the beautifully detailed dinner plates. White pumpkins are peppered throughout the table, adding depth to the design without taking away from the fiery autumnal centerpiece that resides at the heart of the table. White pumpkin-shaped soup tureens are the perfect unexpected complement that are sure to bring joy to your guests.",
