          "body": "Holiday gift shopping season is in full swing. And while it can be great fun to find that big-ticket item on your favorite person's list, not every purchase needs to be a splurge. Sometimes, it really is the little things! From stocking stuffers to gift exchanges, smaller gifts are often the ones that show that we're really paying attention to what our family and friends love. And these Amazon finds are all under $25!\n\nWhether you're on a budget, shopping for an office swap, or just need that one last little something, these gifts are sure to please. We've got something for the home cook and the WFH hustler as well as the camping enthusiast and the friend who just wants to camp out on the couch and watch TV. There's a blanket you might just want to keep for yourself, and a propagation station that will surprise even your most greenery-obsessed friend. And best yet? They'll all please your wallet too!",
